If you are a MT get the Frostbringer and for off hand go Shortblade of Lightning. The Shortblade adds 105 hit points to the Fleshgrinders 75 ( unless you happen to be one of those Tanks who have maxed out your Stamina ).<br>
<br>
As a MT in my guild I use Blade of Carnage main hand and Shortblade of Lightning off hand because I couldnt care less about the fleshy's 160dd proc but care a great deal about having an extra 30 hit points.<br>
<br>
